          "id": "8nqrxrxfwyjk",
          "status": "identified",
          "body": "Trello continues to experience slowdowns and failures that are affecting comment operations, including creating and deleting comments.\n\nOur teams continue to work on the issue resolution, while it is taking longer than expected. We will provide more updates within the next 8 hours or sooner once we have further information to share.",
